{"tid":2341464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"納指新規定上市公司董事會必須有一名女性及一名LGBTQ人士","createTime":"2020-12-26T11:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T15:18:35.000Z","uid":14075,"like":23,"dislike":383,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"cdccddc9b2c65a8d5ab0632daf184a425c744566","tid":2341464,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"Nasdaq Joins Goldman in Corporate Push for More Diverse Boards<br />\n<br />\nNasdaq Inc. plans to require more diversity on boards of directors, the latest push by corporate America to encourage change as regulatory requirements remain unlikely in a gridlocked Washington.<br />\n<br />\nUnder its proposed rules, most companies listed on Nasdaq&rsquo;s U.S. exchange would have to include <span class=\"red\">at least one director who identifies as female and one who identifies as an underrepresented minority or LGBTQ, Nasdaq said in a statement Tuesday. </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-01/nasdaq-plans-to-require-more-diversity-on-listed-company-boards\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-12-01%2Fnasdaq-plans-to-require-more-diversity-on-listed-company-boards&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=bf662d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-12-01/nasdaq-plans-to-require-more-diversity-on-listed-company-boards</a>"},{"pid":"6a939029a58be17b468227fb80457fc389589e13","tid":2341464,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"???"},{"pid":"74abecf73dcf098e017330ef09ec68c6bdf41e0b","tid":2341464,"uid":238370,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"搵個董事出櫃咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e444b42d80a558c1f87af399857e7e66bbaccb1a","tid":2341464,"uid":140953,"like":251,"dislike":6,"score":245,"c